fr̃i Nich̃o magr̃o hospital̃ sc̃i Ioh̃is extͣ portã
orientl̃em Oxoñ ⁊ eiusdẽ loci confr̃ib dom̃ quõ
dã Rob̃ti de Swynebrok ⁊ Iuliane ux̾is sue
in ꝑoch̃ om̃i sc̃oꝵ quã quidẽ dom̃ predc̃i Rob̃tꝰ
⁊ Iuliañ de nobis aliqñ tenuerũt. Ita tamẽ
qd̶ predc̃i magist̾ ⁊ eius confr̃es ⁊ eoꝵ succ̃ no
bis ⁊ succ̃ nr̃is idẽ s̾uiciũ faciant quod nobis
predc̃i Rob̃tꝰ ⁊ Iul̃ fac̾e consueu̾ũt uidel̃t ã
nuatĩ quĩq solid̃ ⁊ octo deñ ꝓ om̃i s̾uicõ et
demand̃. Concesserũt etiã predc̃i magr̃i ⁊ eius
confr̃es nobis ⁊ succ̃ nr̃is qd̶ licite possemꝰ
distring̾e feodũ nr̃m qñcũq contig̾it ip̃os in
predc̃i redditꝰ solucõne defic̾e Et ad huiꝰ ex
utraq ꝑte concessionis firmã ⁊ ꝑpetuã memo
riã utraq ꝑs huic scripto in modũ cirographi
confecto sigill̃ cõe dom̃ sue alt̾natĩ apposuit
